TextEng: I will meet your challenge. Speak it.
Me answer challenge. You say it now.
I apologize for disturbing you. I will leave.
Me sorry to wake you. Me go bye now.
I do not jump through hoops! Defend yourself!
Me not play for you! You die... uh... again!
Text: 나 너한테 놀아주지 않아! 너 죽어... 어... 다시!

TextEng: Okay, a clan... uh... Big Duck Clan?
Text: 음, 부족... 어... 큰 오리 부족?

TextEng: The mighty Clan I Don't Have a Clue?
Um... a clan? It maybe... Clan... Famous Guys... in Hats?
Text: 음... 부족? 아마도... 부족... 유명한 놈들... 모자 쓴?

TextEng: Mirialis Clan.
I'll take a shot. Clan Long Since Gone?
I do not know. How would I find out?
Me don't know. How me find out?
That's it? A stupid riddle?
What? You just gots a stupid riddle?
Text: 뭐? 너 그냥 바보 같은 수수께끼 있어?

TextEng: <StartAction>Show Maegel the book you found on the corpse.</Start>
What? OH! Yes, of course it did. Real far.
Text: 뭐? 아! 그래, 당연히 그랬지. 정말 멀리.

TextEng: No, not... uh... YES, far. Real far. Whoo, me tired.
Text: 아니, 아니... 어... 응, 멀어. 정말 멀어. 우, 나 피곤해.

TextEng: I'm sorry. Maybe you have another riddle?
Uh, me sorry. Maybe you gots another riddle?
Text: 어, 나 미안해. 다른 수수께끼 있어?

TextEng: I am sorry for you, but I did answer correctly.
That the way it goes, me guess. So, gimme stuff.
Text: 뭐 그런 거지. 그러니까 물건 줘.

TextEng: If it's any consolation, I am on an important quest.
Text: 위안이 될지 모르겠지만, 난 중요한 임무 중이야.

TextEng: Uh, me on important quest already. Feel better?
Text: 어, 나 이미 중요한 임무 중이야. 기분 나아?

TextEng: Don't blame me. I was just hunting bears.
Text: 날 탓하지 마. 난 그냥 곰 사냥하러 왔어.

TextEng: Me just hunting bears. What you want?
Text: 나 그냥 곰 사냥 중이었어. 너 뭘 원해?
